snippet.title: Kitiplant - Trailer
snippet.description:
Adorable cats work together to solve puzzles in Kitiplant. Guide them through challenging grid-based levels, where they must share resources and carefully manage their energy to restore life to once-dormant forests.

➤ Wishlist Kitiplant on Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2758380/Kitiplant

➤ Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/dXFYmhFnx4
